    <h1>About Us</h1>
    <div class="about">
        Mid - Lin Day Care started life as Mid Craigie Parish Project in 1994, housed in Mid Craigie Parish Church of Scotland and administered in partnership with St. Ninian's Scottish Episcopal Church, Linlathen Community Association and St. Vincent's R.C. Church.<br />
        <img src="http://btckstorage.blob.core.windows.net/site2373/Scrabble.jpg"/>
<ul>
        <li></li>
        <li>It was started to help to alleviate fear and loneliness among older people.<br /></li>
        <li>It quickly grew and is now housed in its own premises, previously called The Rowans.<br /></li>
        <li>It is a Scottish Charity and is still based in one of the Social Inclusion partnership areas of the City of Dundee although serving the whole city.<br /></li>
        <li>We were registered with OSCR as a charitable company limited by guarantee on 9 April 2003.<br /></li>
        <li>We offer quality Day Care facilities for older people with Physical and/or Mental Health problems.<br /></li>
    </ul>
        <br />
       <p> We aim to assist all our service users to maintain as independent a lifestyle as possible and enjoy a better quality of life.</p>
